title: What is the usual elo you are placed with 10/10 on unranked account?
body: And will duo q make much difference?

replies.body:
Bronze 5.

Have fun trying to climb.
I think you get Gold V.
Nah, I've got G5 with complete shit placements think it was 6/10 and gold 3 Mrr, must be higher

Keep in mind that the order of the wins;losses affect the MMR differently. The first matches weight more than the latter ones, so going 6 wins then 4 losses will put you higher up than if you went 4 losses then 6 wins.
